OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud and
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, perhaps a little
OL,7,Fsleet across Shetland, soon clearing
OL,8,Fto leave clear spells and a few
OL,9,Fshowers through the rest of the
OL,10,Fevening and overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FThe odd light shower through
OL,13,Fthe morning, otherwise dry with some
OL,14,Fbright or sunny intervals. Chance of
OL,15,Frain late evening. Cold but the
OL,16,Foccasionally fresh northerly wind
OL,17,Feasing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
